<title><%= title %></title>
<div class="relative min-h-[80vh] flex items-center overflow-hidden fade-in">
    <!-- Background Accents -->
    <div class="absolute top-0 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-full h-full pointer-events-none -z-10">
        <div class="absolute top-[-10%] left-[-10%] w-[50%] h-[50%] bg-primary/20 rounded-full blur-[120px]"></div>
        <div class="absolute bottom-[-10%] right-[-10%] w-[40%] h-[40%] bg-accent/15 rounded-full blur-[100px]"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 py-20 text-center">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-5 py-2.5 rounded-full bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-md border border-slate-200/60 text-slate-600 text-sm font-bold mb-8 shadow-sm">
            <span class="flex h-2.5 w-2.5 rounded-full bg-primary animate-ping relative">
                <span class="absolute inline-flex h-full w-full rounded-full bg-primary opacity-75"></span>
            </span>
            All-in-One AI Productivity Hub
        </div>
        
        <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-black text-secondary tracking-tighter mb-8 leading-[1.1]">
            Optimalkan Pekerjaan <br>
            Dengan <span class="bg-clip-text text-transparent bg-gradient-to-r from-primary to-accent">PuZero AI.</span>
        </h1>
        
        <p class="max-w-2xl mx-auto text-lg md:text-xl text-slate-500 mb-12 leading-relaxed font-medium">
            Platform serba guna yang dirancang untuk membantu Anda mengunduh media, mengolah data, dan meningkatkan produktivitas menggunakan teknologi AI terbaru.
        </p>

        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4">
            <a hx-get="/category" hx-target="#main-content" hx-push-url="true" class="cursor-pointer px-10 py-5 bg-secondary text-white rounded-2xl font-black text-lg hover:bg-slate-800 transition-all shadow-xl shadow-slate-200 flex items-center justify-center gap-3 w-full sm:w-auto active:scale-95 group">
                Mulai Sekarang
                <i class="ph-bold ph-arrow-right group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform"></i>
            </a>
            <a hx-get="/features" hx-target="#main-content" hx-push-url="true" class="px-10 py-5 bg-white border-2 border-slate-100 text-slate-600 rounded-2xl font-bold text-lg hover:border-primary/30 hover:bg-slate-50 transition-all w-full sm:w-auto active:scale-95 flex items-center justify-center cursor-pointer">
                Pelajari Fitur
            </a>
        </div>
        
        <div class="mt-24 grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8 opacity-60 hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500">
            <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-3 hover:-translate-y-1 transition-transform">
                <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-2xl bg-white border border-slate-100 flex items-center justify-center shadow-sm">
                    <i class="ph-bold ph-lightning text-3xl text-amber-500"></i>
                </div>
                <span class="font-bold text-sm text-slate-600 uppercase tracking-widest">Fast Speed</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-3 hover:-translate-y-1 transition-transform">
                <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-2xl bg-white border border-slate-100 flex items-center justify-center shadow-sm">
                    <i class="ph-bold ph-shield-check text-3xl text-emerald-500"></i>
                </div>
                <span class="font-bold text-sm text-slate-600 uppercase tracking-widest">Secure</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-3 hover:-translate-y-1 transition-transform">
                <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-2xl bg-white border border-slate-100 flex items-center justify-center shadow-sm">
                    <i class="ph-bold ph-infinity text-3xl text-blue-500"></i>
                </div>
                <span class="font-bold text-sm text-slate-600 uppercase tracking-widest">Unlimited</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-3 hover:-translate-y-1 transition-transform">
                <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-2xl bg-white border border-slate-100 flex items-center justify-center shadow-sm">
                    <i class="ph-bold ph-currency-circle-dollar text-3xl text-primary"></i>
                </div>
                <span class="font-bold text-sm text-slate-600 uppercase tracking-widest">100% Free</span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
